                        “NATO in an Era of Global Competition” - A Norwegian perspective</a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[26.06.2014]</p>
                <p>
                    Atlantic Council Conference, June 25th 2014, Washington DC</p>
                
                
                
                
