        <div class="ArticleView">
            <a href="/en/dep/fd/press-centre/Press-releases/20141/Historic-mission-in-Syria-nears-conclusion.html?id=764309" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/imgpreviews/00/00/04/09/40923_img___1403621793.png" alt="" title="" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fd/press-centre/Press-releases/20141/Historic-mission-in-Syria-nears-conclusion.html?id=764309" title="">
                        Historic mission in Syria nears conclusion</a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[23.06.2014]</p>
                <p>
                    ‘I am proud of the way in which the Norwegian Armed Forces have carried out their part of the mission. Removing these weapons from Syria has been vital for ensuring that they cannot be used against the civilian population or fall into the wrong hands. The efforts of our Armed Forces are an important contribution to international peace and security. Although the operation has taken longer than first anticipated, Norway has remained determined throughout to see it through to its conclusion,’ said Minister of Defence Ine Eriksen Søreide.</p>
                
                
                
                
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <hr class="seperator" />
    
        <div class="ArticleView">
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fd/whats-new/Speeches-and-articles/311133-speeches-and-articles-by-senior-m/2014/German-Norwegian-Defence-and-security-co-operation-seminar-Snaroya-June-3-2014.html?id=761524" title="">
                        German-Norwegian Defence and security co-operation seminar, Snarøya, June 3 2014</a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[03.06.2014]</p>
                <p>
                    Morten Tiller, Norwegian National Armaments Director, presented these remarks at the German-Norwegian Defence and security co-operation seminar, Snarøya, June 3, 2014.</p>
                
                
                
                
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <hr class="seperator" />
    
        <div class="ArticleView">
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fd/whats-new/Speeches-and-articles/Speeches-and-articles-by-other-apolitica/taler-og-artikler-av-statssekretar-oyste/2014/Speech-at-the-Norwegian-American-Defence-Conference-2014.html?id=761295" title="">
                        Speech at the Norwegian-American Defence Conference 2014</a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[24.05.2014]</p>
                <p>
                    State secretary Øystein Bø held a speech at the Norwegian-American Defence Conference (NADIC) 2014, in Washington D.C. - "Innovation in Times of Austerity". At the NADIC conference Bø also met with Senator John McCain.  </p>
                
                
                
                
            </div>
        </div>
    
