                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[22.05.2014]</p>
                <p>
                    Minister of Defence Ine Eriksen Søreide held this speech at Nordic Defence Industry Seminar, Sundvolden, May 20th 2014. </p>
                
                
                
                
            </div>
        </div>
    
