        <div class="ArticleView">
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/fd/press-centre/Press-releases/20141/Norwegian-general-becomes-the-first-female-UN-force-commander.html?id=759129" title="">
                        Norwegian general becomes the first female UN force commander</a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[12.05.2014]</p>
                <p>
                    Major General Kristin Lund was today appointed military commander of the UN peace keeping force in Cyprus (UNFICYP). Major General Lund becomes the first female force commander of a UN peacekeeping operation.</p>
                
                
                
                
            </div>
